\begin{frame}{Course objectives}
\pause
\begin{itemize}
\item Students will approach a research question thinking like a social scientist; \pause
\item Builds on foundations of descriptive and causal inference introduced in fall SSI I, with respect to both experimental and observational data \pause
\item and the statistical methods, software introduced in winter SSI II. \pause
\item Further exploration of how to design a study; \pause
\item Present results; \pause
\item Use data visualization effectively. 
\end{itemize}

\end{frame}


