\begin{frame}{Course objectives}

By the end of the quarter, you should be able to \dots\pause
\begin{itemize}
\item Apply the tools you have learned so far in this sequence (data analysis, programming, research design, hypothesis testing)\pause
\item Use those tools and additional writing skills in producing a polished piece of research \pause
\item Design and conduct an original experiment and analyze the results\pause
\item Understand better the differences between observational and experimental research\pause
\item Discuss some important issues in climate change policy and politics
\end{itemize}

